value.0: I suppose the one needing help is not me, but a dear friend. As you may already know, some of the druids have set out in order to find out what's wrong with the Spirit of the Woods.

One of those druids is Orlane, a childhood friend of mine. They have not returned for quite a while. I fear very much for her safety, so I was wondering if you could go and seek her out. She's a halfling, so perhaps she is hiding in some crevice, away from danger.
I know that you have many tasks before you, but please keep an eye out for her.
Thank you! I shall await here for any news.
I was wondering if you needed help with something.
